org.chronos.chronograph.api.builder.graph

Interface ChronoGraphBaseBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChronoGraphBaseBuilderImpl

    public interface ChronoGraphBaseBuilder
    This class acts as the first step in the fluent ChronoGraph builder API.

    You can get access to an instance of this class via ChronoGraphFactory.create().
